<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>登録教科書カタログ | 慶應教科書フリマ</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        keio: {
                            blue: '#002F6C',
                            red: '#9E0B0E',
                            gold: '#C5A059',
                            dark: '#0B132B'
                        }
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Noto Sans JP', 'sans-serif'],
                        serif: ['Noto Serif JP', 'serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .keio-stripe {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #002F6C 42%, #9E0B0E 42%, #9E0B0E 58%, #002F6C 58%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between">

    <!-- Top Tricolor Pennant Stripe -->
    <div class="keio-stripe h-1.5 w-full sticky top-0 z-50"></div>

    <!-- Navigation Header -->
    <header class="bg-white border-b border-slate-100 shadow-sm sticky top-1.5 z-40">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5 group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-keio-blue to-keio-red rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-md transition-transform group-hover:scale-105">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="M4 20L10 14M20 4L14 10" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        <path d="M10 14L13 11L11 9L8 12L7 15L10 14Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
                        <path d="M14 10L11 13L13 15L16 12L17 9L14 10Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="font-serif font-extrabold text-base sm:text-lg text-keio-blue leading-tight tracking-wider">
                        慶應教科書フリマ
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest -mt-0.5">
                        Keio Book Loop
                    </p>
                </div>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/" class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-keio-blue flex items-center gap-1 bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                ← フリマホームに戻る
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-4xl w-full mx-auto px-4 py-10">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden relative p-6 sm:p-8">
            <div class="keio-stripe h-1 w-full absolute top-0 left-0"></div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold text-keio-blue tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-keio-red rounded-full"></span>
                    登録教科書マスターカタログ
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">本フリマプラットフォームに登録されている公式指定教科書のマスターリストです。出品時や検索時の基準となります。</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Table of Books -->
            <div class="overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 rounded-xl">
                <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-slate-100 text-left text-xs sm:text-sm">
                    <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-400 font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]">
                        <tr>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4">教科書タイトル</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4">指定講義・科目</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-right">新品定価</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100 font-medium text-slate-700 bg-white">
                        <% books.forEach(book => { %>
                            <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50/50 transition-colors">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-800"><%= book.title %></td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-slate-500">
                                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
                                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-keio-red"></span>
                                        <%= book.courseName %>
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-keio-blue">¥<%= book.originalPrice.toLocaleString() %></td>
                            </tr>
                        <% }) %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-slate-100 text-center">
                <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-keio-blue hover:bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs transition-colors shadow-md">
                    フリマで教科書を検索する
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 py-6 text-center text-slate-400 text-[10px] tracking-wider">
        &copy; 2026 慶應教科書フリマ (Keio Book Loop) . All Rights Reserved.<br>
        <span class="text-[9px] mt-1 inline-block text-slate-300">「実学の精神」に基づき、塾生同士の知の循環をサポートします。</span>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>